-- U.K. Stocks Gain, Erasing Earlier Drop; Benchmark FTSE 100 Climbs 0.6%
-- Andrew Rummer
-- 2010-07-22T09:29:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/u-k-stocks-rise-for-second-day-erasing-drop-capita-invensys-lead-gains.html

          
          
             U.K. stocks rose for a second day as
Capita Group Plc and Invensys Plc advanced. The FTSE 100 Index
climbed 0.6 percent to 5,243.61 at 10:27 a.m. in London, erasing
an earlier decline of as much as 0.7 percent.  
          
          


  


        